Follow these steps:    ● Code a Java program that will meet part of the client’s specifications.You don’t have to have to
meet all the client specifications at this stage. This Capstone project will be your first deliverable for Poised. You will 
build upon this program in later Capstone projects. For this program, you should:  o Create a class that will be used to
create a project object.  o Create a class that will be used to create person (e.g. architect, building contractor, etc.) 
objects.  o Write a program that will allow a user to:  ▪ Capture the details that are used to create a new project 
object.  ▪ Change the due date of the project.  ▪ Change the total amount of the fee paid to date.  ▪ Update a 
contractor’s contact details.  ▪ Finalise the project. 
